Major News Items in Leading Pakistani Newspapers
ISLAMABAD , December 28 ( Xinhua ) -- The following are major news items in leading Pakistani English newspapers Monday .
The News :
-- Army was called out Sunday in Bannu , 275 km south of Peshwar , after the killing of five persons and injuries to 20 others due to riots sparked by the killing of a 15-year-old boy by a police constable , who tried to molest him but shot him dead on resistance .
The Nation :
-- President Rafiq Tarar Sunday brushed aside reports that his powers have been curtailed , saying the recent act passed by the parliament to make slight amendments to official regulations and did not harm the Presidential powers .
